<div class="quizholder">
  <table class="sumbinary" id="questionholder" >
    <tr class="sumline1 sumcolumns" ><th>&nbsp;</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><th>&nbsp;</th></tr>
    <tr class="sumline2" ><th>+</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><th>&nbsp;</th></tr>
    <tr class="sumresult binaryinput"><th>=</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><th><button class="sumzerofill btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-unchecked" aria-hidden="true"></span>Blanks to 0's</button></th></tr>
    <tr class="sumcarry binarycarryinput" ><th>Carry</th><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp; </td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td><td class="invalid">&nbsp;</td><th>&nbsp;</th></tr>
  </table>
  <label class="overflowlabel" for="sumexplain">Explain any overflow</label> <input type="text" class="sumexplain" length="100" size="40"/><br />
  <button class="sumcheck btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Check Answer</button>
  <button class="sumzerofill btn btn-default" id="sumzerofill2"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-unchecked" aria-hidden="true"></span>Blanks to 0's</button>
  <button class="sumnextquestion btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-forward" aria-hidden="true"></span>Next Question</button>
  <button class="sumhint btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>Get a Hint</button>
  <button class="sumskip btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-fast-forward" aria-hidden="true"></span>Skip Question</button>
  
  <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">
    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      Guidance
  </button>
      
  <button class="sumend btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-print" aria-hidden="true"></span>Finish Exercise</button>
  
  <div class="sumfeedback">&nbsp;</div>
  <table class="scores">
    <tr>
      <th>Current Score</th><td class="sumscore">&nbsp;</td>
      <th>Exam Marks</th><td class="summarks">&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<div id="dump">
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Guidance</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <h3>Using the quiz</h3>
            <p>The <span class="sumresult">grey area</span> and Carry row responds to mouse clicks. Clicking once will set it to "1", clicking again set it to "0". (You can just fill in the "1"s and use the <button class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Blanks to 0's</button> button).</p>
            <p>You can also use "1" "0" and "c" on the keyboard to type the answer from the right</p>
            <p>Then click <button class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Check Answer</button> to check it. If you have not filled in the 0's that will be offered (but will happen automatically after a delay). If there are problems with your answer <button class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-question-sign" aria-hidden="true"></span>Get a Hint</button> will appear, click it for in-depth guidance. Then click <button class=" btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-forward" aria-hidden="true"></span>Next Question</button> to move on (again this will also happen automatically after a delay)</p>
        <h3>Finishing the exercise</h3>    
            <p>The questions will get harder as you go. When you have praciticed enough online please click the <button class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-print" aria-hidden="true"></span>Finish Exercise</button> button, and print out the work sheet to do on paper. And hand that in asap.</p>
        <h3>Doing the questions</h3>    
            <p>Remember to work from the right, adding one column at a time (and marking the carry row of the next column to the left if you need to)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{{{raw-helper}}}}        
<script id="entry-template" type="text/x-handlebars-template">
<html>
    <head>
        <link href="css/binary-addition.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all">
    <style>    
        .printsumline1>td{
            width:2em;
        }
        
        .printsumresult>td, .printsumcarry>td{
            border-top-width: 2px;
            border-top-style: solid;
            border-top-color: black;
            
        }
    </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Binary Addition - Paper Quiz</h1>
        
        <p>Please print this sheet out and complete these questions by hand.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> ________________________________ </p>
        
        {{#aQuestions}}
        <div class="quizholder">
            <h2>Question {{iQuestion}}</h2>
            <table class="sumbinary" id="questionholder" >
                <tr class="printsumline1 " ><th>&nbsp;</th><td>&nbsp;</td>{{#each aLine1}}<td>{{this}}</td>{{/each}}</tr>
                <tr class="printsumline2" ><th>+</th><td>&nbsp;</td>{{#each aLine2}}<td>{{this}}</td>{{/each}}</tr>
                <tr class="printsumresult"><th>=</th><td colspan="9">&nbsp;</td></tr>
                <tr class="printsumcarry" ><th>Carry</th><td colspan="9">&nbsp;</td></tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        {{/aQuestions}}
        
        <h2>Online Results</h2>
        <p>    Score = {{iCurrentScore}}<br />
            Marks = {{iCurrentMark}} / {{iMaxMark}}
            </p>
    </body>
</html>

</script>
{{{{/raw-helper}}}}
